## Task 2: 创建 UpgradeTask007

**Files:**
- Create: `src/main/java/com/yottastudios/jira/upgrade/v1/UpgradeTask007.java`
- Modify: `src/main/resources/atlassian-plugin.xml`

Create UpgradeTask007.java:
```java
package com.yottastudios.jira.upgrade.v1;

import com.atlassian.activeobjects.external.ActiveObjects;
import com.atlassian.activeobjects.external.ActiveObjectsUpgradeTask;
import com.atlassian.activeobjects.external.ModelVersion;
import com.yottastudios.jira.ao.Template;
import com.yottastudios.jira.ao.TemplateGroup;

public class UpgradeTask007 implements ActiveObjectsUpgradeTask {

	@Override
	public ModelVersion getModelVersion() {
		return ModelVersion.valueOf("7");
	}

	@Override
	public void upgrade(ModelVersion modelVersion, ActiveObjects ao) {
		ao.migrate(TemplateGroup.class, Template.class);
	}
}
```

In atlassian-plugin.xml, after the line `<upgradeTask>com.yottastudios.jira.upgrade.v1.UpgradeTask006</upgradeTask>`, add:
```xml
        <upgradeTask>com.yottastudios.jira.upgrade.v1.UpgradeTask007</upgradeTask>
```

